# ── Per-run working state ────────────────────────────────────────────
# loop/<target>/ — golden sets, staging prompts, history/failure logs and turn
# state produced by each agent-coach run. Reproducible working state, not
# source; kept on disk but never committed.
/loop/

# Local usecase inputs (target prompts, golden sets, direction docs) — kept on
